    <item>
      <title>马斯克施压 英国宣布对儿童强奸团伙展开调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/uk-announces-probes-into-child-rape-gangs-after-musk-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在亿万富翁埃隆马斯克加大对政府施压，要求对这一存在数十年的问题进行全国性调查的几周后，英国内政大臣伊维特库珀宣布对所谓的儿童性侵团伙展开一系列地方调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/uk-announces-probes-into-child-rape-gangs-after-musk-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 16:02:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
